title: Man City beat Real Madrid to pile pressure on Alonso
subtitle: Goals from Nico O'Reilly and Erling Haaland give Manchester City a 2-1 victory over Real Madrid at the Bernabeu, to pile pressure on Madrid manager Xabi Alonso.
full_text: Goals from Nico O'Reilly and Erling Haaland give Manchester City a 2-1 victory over Real Madrid at the Bernabeu, to pile pressure on Madrid manager Xabi Alonso.
